{"tid":2179210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華潤旗下VanGO突停售《蘋果》  稱正常商業決定 阿布泰光榮冰室：我哋賣","createTime":"2020-08-29T03:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T03:38:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"169df8dbb328d517a0fa8b1c0e4917c0ef2b061c","tid":2179210,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/KXXIKTSRWZCPVNHUS54VN7Q5J4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FKXXIKTSRWZCPVNHUS54VN7Q5J4%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=27df833d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FKXXIKTSRWZCPVNHUS54VN7Q5J4%2F&h=e8ce2385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/KXXIKTSRWZCPVNHUS54VN7Q5J4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華潤旗下VanGO突停售《蘋果》 <br />\n稱正常商業決定 阿布泰光榮冰室：我哋賣<br />\n<br />\n【商業打壓】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：讀者繼續撐 議員憂變全港封殺<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國企封殺《蘋果》，華潤萬家旗下VanGO便利店昨突然停售《蘋果日報》，受影響報章約千份，VanGO指屬「公司正常商業決定」。有學者視為中資進一步封殺《蘋果》行動，事發半日後黃店阿布泰國生活百貨指「你唔賣，我哋賣」，宣佈旗下11間分店今天起賣《蘋果》，每間入貨100份，抵銷VanGO停賣的數量。另外黃店光榮冰室旗下五店亦於下周一起售賣《蘋果》。<br />\n<br />\n華潤萬家是中央直屬的國有控股企業集團，根據資料，旗下VanGO便利店在本港有40多間分店，其中30間售賣《蘋果日報》。VanGO facebook專頁回應本報查詢時表示「沒有《蘋果日報》」，稱停賣屬「公司正常商業決定」。<br />\n<br />\n今次停賣事件十分突然，昨晨《蘋果》發行部如常將報紙送到VanGO，但店員稱接到公司通告昨天起不賣《蘋果》，但無解釋原。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ehCDdOqmdH6LDac4sP7jnluo33w=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JMHYWS653RGB5O7KFZA7OME5RQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FehCDdOqmdH6LDac4sP7jnluo33w%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJMHYWS653RGB5O7KFZA7OME5RQ.jpg&h=d3aa3be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■VanGO為國企華潤萬家旗下便利店。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林景楠：好光榮有得賣<br />\n<br />\n在封殺事件發生半日後，多次就社會議題發聲的阿布泰國生活百貨宣佈今天起在旗下11間分店售賣《蘋果日報》，在facebook。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，並非全部巿民透過網絡或app收看新聞資訊，仍有部份巿民會看紙媒，「咁嘅情況下，我好光榮咁講一句，我公司都有《蘋果。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n阿布泰創辦人林景楠曾任海關關員，2015年因曾在「光復沙田」示威現場接受電視台訪問，被海關無理解僱。其後他創立阿布泰。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本月初，華潤資本牽頭的財團落實收購連鎖超市City&rsquo;super六成半權益。據知，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：表態換取政治資本<br />\n<br />\n港大經濟及工商管理學院助理講師阮穎嫻表示，《蘋果》銷情一向不俗，下架「咁就一係表態，一係就有壓力囉」。她認為商家是。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EEDK1zr0uWzKSKm8qebv1eKQGwo=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJPFMSRXUFAZ7DN2EIYIFMWSZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEEDK1zr0uWzKSKm8qebv1eKQGwo%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJPFMSRXUFAZ7DN2EIYIFMWSZE.jpg&h=9ad80a89&s={SIZE}\" />                            <br />\n■記者到VanGO其中一間分店查看，發現貨架上《蘋果日報》標示牌被放到最底層。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/poq79aYGK2NsXfu9a1z5F4-vpOs=/2482x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R5JG5WJKNBDRDPLZP4D3JCB3N4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpoq79aYGK2NsXfu9a1z5F4-vpOs%3D%2F2482x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR5JG5WJKNBDRDPLZP4D3JCB3N4.jpg&h=047ae8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■阿布泰昨在fb發帖，表示旗下11間分店今日起售賣《蘋果日報》。"},{"pid":"f74a8c5dbde382cd087e059574d147699c25544b","tid":2179210,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"爆買既大時代到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafe190f94891e722d3a224791207108302def2c","tid":2179210,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"唔知渣哥有冇得賣？<br />\n<br />\n呀可能d枱拎曬黎做生意冇位放<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2826c57ea0492db58c3dda23299de583a0905991","tid":2179210,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"張老闆如果可以 可否賣埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}